dc_description_s: This data group represents zoning for Polk County, Wisconsin in 2019 and includes the layers 'Polk_General_2019' and 'Polk_Shoreland_2019'.[Shoreland: This dataset designates the zoning district for geographical areas in Polk County. The data set is a compilation of multiple internal data sets including 'ZoningComp', 'ZoningShoreland', 'ZoneGenPur', and 'ZoningWet'.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.For access to the most current data for this county, please visit: https://www.co.polk.wi.us/index.asp?SEC=A94D4B49-F047-496F-A7B9-A259974E7E6F&Type=B_BASIC
